{
  "permissions": {
    "allow": [
      "Bash(npm run:*)",
      "Bash(npm install:*)",
      "Bash(npm uninstall:*)",
      "Bash(npm run dev:*)",
      "Bash(npm run build:*)",
      "Bash(npm run lint:*)",
      "Bash(npx tsc --noEmit:*)",
      "Bash(git add:*)",
      "Bash(git commit:*)",
      "Bash(git push:*)",
      "Bash(git status:*)",
      "Bash(git diff:*)",
      "Bash(curl:*)",
      "Bash(ls:*)",
      "Bash(node:*)",
      "Bash(git commit -m \"$\\(cat <<''EOF''\nfeat: Claude Code 표준 설정 추가\n\n- CLAUDE.md 생성 \\(개발 워크플로우, 코딩 컨벤션\\)\n- Commands 추가 \\(typecheck, lint-fix, build-check 등 5개\\)\n- Agents 추가 \\(build-validator, code-reviewer 등 4개\\)\n- settings.local.json 업데이트 \\(hooks, permissions\\)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>\nEOF\n\\)\")",
      "Bash(find:*)",
      "WebSearch",
      "Bash(gh:*)",
      "Bash(git remote add:*)",
      "Bash(vercel --version:*)"
    ],
    "deny": [
      "Bash(rm -rf node_modules:*)",
      "Bash(rm -rf .next:*)"
    ],
    "ask": []
  },
  "hooks": {
    "PostToolUse": [
      {
        "matcher": "Write|Edit",
        "hooks": [
          {
            "type": "command",
            "command": "npm run lint || true"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
